                    </div>
                    <div class="card-info">
                        <h3>Flock</h3>
                        <p>Flock transforms everyday visits into meaningful experiences where businesses create
                            location-based check-ins, personalized rewards, and exclusive offers. At the same time,
                            customers enjoy a simple, engaging way to earn points, redeem coupons, and get rewarded for
                            every visit
                        </p>
                        <button class="card-pill-btn">Discover more</button>
                    </div>
                </div>

